data.description: This immaculately maintained, one-owner home in a wonderful White Bear Lake neighborhood is a rare find! Located on a beautiful 1/4 acre lot, the home has a fantastic front & back yard with landscaping and mature trees. This home is close to parks, schools, and everything White Bear Lake has to offer. Inside you will find gorgeous, original hardwood floors that have been recently refinished. There are 3 spacious bedrooms on one level and a completely tiled full bathroom. The inviting living room has a huge picture window that lets in all the light. Step out to the deck from the kitchen and enjoy the convenience of grilling and spending time in the backyard. The lower level includes a spacious family room with a brick wood-burning fireplace. The unfinished basement is great for storage or could be finished for more square footage. Do not wait to view this fantastic home!
